Description:
Low maintenance living, Close to all amenities!
This low maintenance home is the ideal start for first home buyers or investors and is also great for people looking to downsize.
Located in Dandenong Central, approximately 1 km from Dandenong Plaza and Dandenong Market, everything you need is within a short walk.
This home offers three spacious bedrooms, large lounge, and large kitchen with meals area. A front verandah overlooks the front garden, whilst a fully fenced, private rear yard offers ample space for kids or pets with access to a single lock up garage.
The home is the front one of only two on the block and is within walking distance to all of Dandenong amenities as well as providing easy access to Princes Hwy and Eastlink.

Description:
Modern 4 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom Townhouse in Central Location
Step in and smell the fresh paint as you are walking into this immaculate four bedroom townhouse.
If you are looking for your first home or investment, this ticks all the boxes. Be quick though as this property will be snapped up fast!
Home comprised of;
- Spacious lounge which leads to kitchen meals area
- Kitchen with plenty of cupboard space and gas cooking
- Four bedrooms with built in robes to 3 of the rooms
- Master bedroom with full ensuite and mirrored built in robes
- Bedroom downstairs also has full ensuite which can be 4th bedroom or a study
- Central bathroom upstairs
- Laundry with built in cupboards and access to back yard
- Double lock up garage
- Secured rear yard with very low maintenance gardens
Extra features in the home include;
- Ducted heating
- New Holland blinds
- Satellite dish
- Security doors
- Fly screens
- Security lights
- Small garden shed
- Storage under stairs
Walking distance to Dandenong High School, primary schools, bus stops and local shops. Only a short drive to Dandenong Plaza, Market, and freeways.
This home will certainly impress the fussiest of buyers.
PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT INSPECTIONS. Call Linda or Jack today before you see a SOLD sticker!

Description:
CONSIDER THE OPTIONS ON 621SQM APPROX.
Placed on the high side of the road on 621sqm approx., this comfortable family home invites obvious consideration as a multi-unit development site, whilst its well-planned dimensions provide ample scope to extend/renovate or alternatively lease out whilst plans are made (STCA).
Introduced via a wide 19m (approx.) frontage, the home’s neat layout is beautifully lit with natural light and offers a large L-shaped lounge and dining room with corner windows, a gas heater and the appeal of high ceilings. While the kitchen is perfectly functional for today and includes an upright Simpson oven/cooktop and windows that overlook the backyard.
Carried along the hallway, there are three bedrooms (two with built-in-robes), accompanied by a family bathroom, separate toilet and laundry that opens onto the large north facing backyard with open lawn area and side driveway access.
Situated in a location that affords outstanding convenience, with quality primary and secondary schools, Dandenong Plaza and Market, reserves and trains all within walking distance.

Description:
EXPLORE YOUR OPTIONS - CENTRAL DANDENONG!
Ideally situated in the very heart of Dandenong, within walking distance to the Market, Plaza, Hospital and Schools, you'll find this perfect option to renovate and restore the home to its former glory.
Zoned Residential Growth Zone - Schedule 1 and sitting on a block of 566m2, it also offers the option to develop (STCA).
The accommodation offers two or three bedrooms or optional lounge. The bedrooms have built in robes with the main having a ceiling fan. A spacious family/dining with adjoining study, functional kitchen with gas cooking and plenty of cupboards. There's a family bathroom, separate toilet and laundry. Other features include 2.7m ceilings, art deco' ceiling roses, decorative cornices, two open fire places and ducted heating. Outside you have a small rear verandah, plenty of off-street parking and a carport.
CLOSE TO ALL CENTRAL DANDENONG HAS TO OFFER!
